{"tid":2215200,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"王家衛新作《重慶森林2020》正式獲准拍攝","createTime":"2020-09-23T23:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T13:52:56.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":132,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9f8e8a94e107035cd415cb262d00fd46e4b9fc","tid":2215200,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T23:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ooJwpV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ooJwpV.jpg&h=ab7840a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新浪娛樂訊9月23日，國家電影局2020年4月備案、立項公示出爐。王家衛新作《重慶森林2020》正式獲准拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n故事梗概為：90s香港，失戀警察223偶遇金發女殺手，一夜共渡短暫溫暖二人。也經歷失戀的警察663，生活漸被一位闖入的&ldquo;夢中人&rdquo;改變。2036年，少年小千和阿May不甘被基因配對牽手，執意找尋自己的&ldquo;命運&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.sina.cn/film/chinese/2020-09-23/detail-iivhuipp6066985.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.sina.cn%2Ffilm%2Fchinese%2F2020-09-23%2Fdetail-iivhuipp6066985.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=ddb5077f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ent.sina.cn/film/chinese/2020-09-23/detail-iivhuipp6066985.d.html?from=wap</a>"},{"pid":"51d66b9abcce70eac74b9450e02b29abd751f590","tid":2215200,"uid":104804,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T23:28:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔係香港拍"},{"pid":"621f868da846244562822f52184109cfd4661a8b","tid":2215200,"uid":141151,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"quote":{"pid":"51d66b9abcce70eac74b9450e02b29abd751f590","tid":2215200,"uid":104804,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T23:28:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔係香港拍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T23:29:28.000Z","msg":"去重慶ge森林拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e313d42dd04940a5318740eb9939dfa520a658","tid":2215200,"uid":188282